      <title>PayPal 改进 Venmo 业务资料，提供现金返还奖励</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/paypal-revamps-venmo-business-profiles-offers-cash-back-rewards</link>
      <description><![CDATA[PayPal Holdings Inc. 推出了多项产品增强功能，包括通过 PayPal 应用程序赚取现金的机会，这家支付公司的首席执行官试图重振这家难以保持竞争力的公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/paypal-revamps-venmo-business-profiles-offers-cash-back-rewards</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 17:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国称中国和俄罗斯掩饰其卫星构成的攻击威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/china-russia-disguise-threats-posed-by-satellites-us-space-force-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据美国太空部队的一份新报告，中国和俄罗斯发射了旨在检查和修理其他航天器的卫星，但也可能被用来攻击美国的资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/china-russia-disguise-threats-posed-by-satellites-us-space-force-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 17:01:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>IT 公司遭遇网络攻击，瑞典央行向警方求助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/sweden-riksbank-turns-to-police-after-ransomware-hits-tietoevry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自上周末以来，芬兰软件公司 Tietoevry Oyj 的客户因勒索软件攻击而导致部分 IT 系统无法访问，瑞典央行已向警方提交了一份报告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/sweden-riksbank-turns-to-police-after-ransomware-hits-tietoevry</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 16:45:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华盛顿地区人工智能就业岗位随着联邦机构拥抱新技术而激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/washington-area-enjoys-ai-job-surge-as-feds-embrace-new-tech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[最新研究表明，随着政府及其承包商拥抱新兴技术，美国首都正在抢占大量需要人工智能技能的新工作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/washington-area-enjoys-ai-job-surge-as-feds-embrace-new-tech</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Meta 耗资 8 亿美元在印第安纳州建造新的人工智能数据中心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/meta-building-new-800-million-ai-focused-data-center-in-indiana</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc. 正在印第安纳州建设一座耗资 8 亿美元的数据中心，该数据中心将进行优化以处理人工智能服务，这标志着 Facebook 母公司为获得新技术优势而做出的最新尝试。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/meta-building-new-800-million-ai-focused-data-center-in-indiana</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 15:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Tinder 要求哥伦比亚用户在致命吸毒后审查匹配对象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/tinder-tells-colombia-users-to-vet-matches-after-fatal-druggings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Tinder 向哥伦比亚用户发出安全警告，因为越来越多的犯罪分子使用这款流行的约会应用来引诱受害者下毒和抢劫。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/tinder-tells-colombia-users-to-vet-matches-after-fatal-druggings</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 15:12:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>微软在游戏领域裁员 1,900 人，其中包括动视暴雪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/microsoft-cuts-1-900-jobs-in-gaming-including-at-activision</link>
      <description><![CDATA[微软公司将在其视频游戏部门裁员 1,900 人，其中包括动视暴雪公司，该公司在去年底完成的收购中以 690 亿美元收购了该部门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/microsoft-cuts-1-900-jobs-in-gaming-including-at-activision</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 14:36:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管订户流失，康卡斯特仍实现盈利增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/comcast-earnings-top-forecasts-while-cable-losses-mount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[康卡斯特公司(Comcast Corp.)公布的盈利超出华尔街预期后，股价创下六个月来最大涨幅。尽管这家美国有线电视巨头的订户数量持续下降，但情况仍然如此。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/comcast-earnings-top-forecasts-while-cable-losses-mount</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 12:00:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Byju 的贷方在错过付款后提交破产申请</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/lenders-to-india-startup-byju-s-submit-insolvency-filing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在印度教育初创公司 Byju’s Alpha 未能偿还 12 亿美元贷款后，该公司的贷款人提交了破产申请。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/lenders-to-india-startup-byju-s-submit-insolvency-filing</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 11:22:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>IBM 给出 2024 年乐观前景，股价创 20 年来最大涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/ibm-sees-strong-2024-free-cash-flow-plans-job-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际商业机器公司 (International Business Machines Corp.) 尽管预计将减少就业岗位，但对 2024 年收入和现金流做出积极展望，股价创下 20 多年来最大单日涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/ibm-sees-strong-2024-free-cash-flow-plans-job-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 21:09:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
